caption.center: PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. ROGER DUANE

opinion.opinion_text:
SC: 127062, COA: 248686, Eaton CC: 02-020399-FC.
On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 27, 2004 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
